message.body: Anything fun going on this weekend?
(1/2)Haha! San Francisco is fun anytime of the year. There's always something going on. Went on a marine wildlife eco tour yesterday. It was like a 2-hr boat
(2/2)ride where we saw seals and other sea creatures
There's a food and wine festival today. So yeah, fun weekend this. How's yours?
The eco tour sounds awesome!! And food and wine make a winning combo.:-)
Nice! The weather's perfect for a bbq here too, you know. Say, have you ever been to the Bay Area?
Yes, been a number of times. Two years ago I worked a promo in the bay area for 5 weeks. We rented a couple rooms in a house in Hayward.
